# Moby's service credentials
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Any KEY=value pair in this file becomes an environment variable
# inside the agent container. Use it for tool CLIs (aws, npm, etc.)
#
# Format: KEY=value  (no spaces around =, no quotes needed)
#
# Examples:
#   AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=AKIA...
#   AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=...
#   NPM_TOKEN=npm_...
#
# Note: GitHub uses OAuth device flow via `gh auth login`.
# No token needed here - just ask Moby to authenticate with GitHub.
# The gh OAuth session is persisted in ~/.mobyclaw/gh/.
#
# Tip: The agent can install tools at runtime. Ask Moby to
# "install the GitHub CLI" and it will run apt-get/curl as needed.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
